    <stitle>STEERABLE DRIVE AXLE END UNIT: FABCO - LUBRICATION</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>LUBRICATION</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <para>Refer to GROUP 10 - LUBRICATION in the CTS-5000 Master Service Manual for recommended lubricants and
                lubrication intervals.
            </para>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
        <svcproc svcproctype="lubricate" graphiccount="0">
            <title>WHEEL BEARINGS</title>
            <para>When lubricating wheel bearings, liberally pack both inner and outer wheel bearings, and ensure that
                the grease has penetrated thoroughly into the cage and roller assembly. Prior to reassembly, coat the
                raceways and interior hub surfaces as well.
            </para>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
